data.description: Welcome to 301 Spyglass Lane located in Broussard. This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is located in the prestigious neighborhood of Le Triomphe Subdivision. This home sits on a corner lot with a 3-car garage. Attention to detail is showcased throughout the residence. The open-concept living area is adorned with soaring ceilings and oversized windows. There is beautiful wallpaper throughout and Brazilian hardwood flooring. The kitchen features granite countertops with plenty of cabinetry and a center island. Theadjacent formal dining area has a view into the sunroom and is ideal for hosting gatherings ordinner parties. The primary suite is spacious and has a master bathroom featuring a walk-in shower and a spa-like soaking tub. The bathroom offers dual vanities and 2 walk-in closets. It has three other generously-sized bedrooms that offer ample space and each is thoughtfully designed with its own unique character. The addition of the sunroom provides plenty of space for entertaining and also has its very own fireplace. Located in a highly sought-after neighborhood, this residence offers an unparalleled lifestyle. It is close to schools, premier shopping and dining options, and convenient access to Highway 90. This property provides the perfect blend of comfort, luxury, and convenience. Call to schedule your showing today!
